Laila El Garaa (Arabic) bụ onye na-eme egwuregwu Paralympic si Morocco na-asọmpi karịsịa na ụdị F40 shot putt events.
O sonyere na afọ 2004 Summer Paralympics na Athens, Gris
N'ebe ahụ, o ritere ihe nrite ọlaọcha na ihe omume ụmụ nwanyị F40 shot putt
O sonyekwara na F40 javelin throw nke ụmụ nwanyị
O mekwara asọmpi na afọ 2008 Summer Paralympics na Beijing, China
N'ebe ahụ, o ritere ọla nchara na ihe omume ụmụ nwanyị F40 shot putt
O sonyekwara na asọmpi F40 nke ụmụ nwanyị.
Ụmụnne ya nwanyị Najat na Hayat bụ ndị nwetara ihe nrite Paralympic.
